Implements APPROVED brief (Codex iter 5 APPROVE, zero P0/P1) for GH#464.

Synthesizer (src/polaris_graph/v30_contract_synthesizer.py):
- build_v30_contract(v6_template, query_slug, question=None) → per_query_report_contract.{slug}
- Schema: v30.1 with required_entities (id/type/required_fields/min_fields_for_completion/
  rendering_slot/url_pattern/anchor) + rendering_slots DICT keyed by slot_id
  (section/subsection_title/ordering/required) + section_order
- Mechanical 1-frame → 1-slot + 1-entity transform from v6 frame_manifest
- Concrete http(s) url_pattern rotated through T1 sources (M-56 fetchable;
  not a regex per Codex iter-4 P1 verification of frame_fetcher.py:780,1046)
- Stable anchor <template_id>:<frame_id>:<slug[:40]>:<sha256_8> as secondary id

actors.py:
- Imports polaris_v6.templates.registry.load_template + build_v30_contract
- Attaches synth output to q["v30_contract_patch"]
- FileNotFoundError + generic Exception both → logger.warning (exc_info=True);
  pipeline-A handles via legacy no-contract path

pipeline-A (scripts/run_honest_sweep_r3.py):
- 5-LOC merge of q["v30_contract_patch"] into _template["per_query_report_contract"]
- Runs AFTER load_scope_template, BEFORE compile_frame / load_report_contract_for_slug
- Non-v6 sweep (q lacking v6_mode) → noop; legacy CLI byte-identical

8 golden fixtures (tests/fixtures/v30_contracts/<template_id>.json):
- ai_sovereignty, canada_us, climate, clinical, defense, housing, trade, workforce
- 5 frames each → 5 entities + 5 slots + section_order

Tests (tests/polaris_graph/test_v30_contract_synthesizer.py): 35/35 pass
- 8× golden fixture match (build output == fixture JSON)
- 8× round-trip via load_report_contract_for_slug (schema_version=v30.1)
- 8× compile_frame produces non-empty evidence_bindings
- 8× M-56 fetchability: every binding has resolvable locator (urlparse scheme+netloc)
- Anchor stability + collision-safety
- url_pattern rotation through T1 (entity[i] == T1[i % len(T1)])
- Empty-T1 fallback returns valid URL

Codex iteration trail:
- Brief iter 1: REQUEST_CHANGES (M55 locator missing + actor template source wrong)
- Brief iter 2: REQUEST_CHANGES (load_scope_template loads yaml not v6 JSON)
- Brief iter 3: REQUEST_CHANGES (anchor-only entities fail M-56)
- Brief iter 4: REQUEST_CHANGES (url_pattern regex not M-56 fetchable)
- Brief iter 5: APPROVE (concrete T1 URL rotation; urlparse validation test)

Full pytest: 1988 passed (1 pre-existing test_demo_smoke isolation failure
unrelated to I-arch-001b; passes when run in isolation pre AND post).

GH#464.

